headline: PINK’s 58% Gains Since 2021 Come From Picking Winners, Not Owning Everything

When tech stocks swing wildly and consumer spending wobbles, healthcare companies keep selling drugs, performing surgeries, and processing insurance claims. That steady demand makes the sector attractive when investors want growth without the full roller coaster. But what if you could get healthcare exposure with a more concentrated bet ...
